    "description": "《从0开始的VUP生活》是一款虚拟主播模拟游戏，您可以在游戏中安排主角的日常生活、直播、交友、阅读八卦、与粉丝互动，最终达成不同的结局。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>内容要素</strong></h2><br><br>◆像素风，所有角色全动态立绘<br><br>◆主播模拟，经营日常<br><br>◆重剧情，多结局，多周目<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/d6f912726a72f938df1bcb2bbdb47a27.poster.avif?t=1752205441\" width=640 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/d6f912726a72f938df1bcb2bbdb47a27.webm?t=1752205441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/d6f912726a72f938df1bcb2bbdb47a27.mp4?t=1752205441\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/2da7299523eaf15be548d5f6426b004d.apng?t=1752205441\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/2da7299523eaf15be548d5f6426b004d.poster.avif?t=1752205441\" class=\"bb_img\" width=207 height=315 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/24cb646090d97d79eb0405ee7d01381b.poster.avif?t=1752205441\" width=207 height=315 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/24cb646090d97d79eb0405ee7d01381b.webm?t=1752205441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>我们的主角</strong></h2>她是一位稍显内向、对自己并不是很自信的少女，但她特别喜欢唱歌；由于父亲是一名杰出的水利工程师，希望她能走相同的道路，要求她念水利工程相关的专业，但她依然想向音乐方向发展，于是父女约定以半年为限，如果主角能在时间内在音乐方面做出成绩就可以继续自己喜欢的工作，如果不行就必须听从父亲的安排进入水利局工作。主角由于学习的专业与音乐无关，所以去音乐工作室应聘屡屡受挫，但她受到一位画师学姐的鼓励，建议她先从虚拟主播开始尝试一下。<br>于是——<br>我们的红龙公主<strong>维奥娜</strong>堂堂出道！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/ec1db5ccf0d7a89e3d4e2af8fe08cebb.apng?t=1752205441\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/ec1db5ccf0d7a89e3d4e2af8fe08cebb.poster.avif?t=1752205441\" class=\"bb_img\" width=300 height=340 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/8183169a0ea2a3d8101bf462efac6896.poster.avif?t=1752205441\" width=300 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/8183169a0ea2a3d8101bf462efac6896.webm?t=1752205441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>她将来会成为歌星吗？会成为百大UP主吗？会成为职业玩家吗？会成为偶像吗？还是回归现实向父亲妥协成为一名水利工程师，偶尔在年会上唱歌一曲...  少女的未来在你的手中...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>她的朋友们</strong></h2>维奥娜在外出/直播期间会遇到许多性格迥异的伙伴与其他虚拟主播，她们也会有各自的故事和不同的结局....<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆捞月亮的咩咩</strong></h2>咩咩自称什么都播的全能型主播，她最为特殊的地方在于总将唐诗宋词挂在嘴边，常常能引经据典，似乎非常有学识，但她的粉丝们反而喜欢用逆天的谐音梗来调戏她；有一天在没有任何动态的状况下，她突然停播了，几周后的复播很多粉丝发现她虽然声音相似但说话方式和性格出现了很大不同，疑似更换了中之人... <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/01bd3ca1890f2987e3606b7d619feea1.apng?t=1752205441\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/01bd3ca1890f2987e3606b7d619feea1.poster.avif?t=1752205441\" class=\"bb_img\" width=300 height=340 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/3062b438b4a394dcfdb0a36cd5146244.apng?t=1752205441\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/3062b438b4a394dcfdb0a36cd5146244.poster.avif?t=1752205441\" class=\"bb_img\" width=300 height=340 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆罗琳社长</strong></h2>罗琳是一位有着较高人气的虚拟主播，非常擅长杂谈，尤其喜欢调戏小雏男，深受男性粉丝的喜爱，在她成名之后建立了现在的<strong>慈善社</strong>，一个虚拟主播的公会，眼光毒辣，签下了许多有潜力的小主播，并将她们成功捧红，虽然经常以资本家自居，但给主播们的条件也还不错。不过嘛... 事情并非一帆风顺.... <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/98288ab9cc7c6bb80c252af345149a67.apng?t=1752205441\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/98288ab9cc7c6bb80c252af345149a67.poster.avif?t=1752205441\" class=\"bb_img\" width=300 height=340 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/29f0e2bb99ec81520dfc8df79ad2a185.poster.avif?t=1752205441\" width=300 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/29f0e2bb99ec81520dfc8df79ad2a185.webm?t=1752205441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆坷诺Keno</strong></h2>坷诺是一位有着小恶魔性格、特别喜欢整活的虚拟主播：断头、劈叉、走红毯甚至直播睡觉，她的直播间里总是不乏笑料。但随着某件突发事件后，她遭遇了大量炎上和网暴，同时全平台开始严禁整活，就像当年ASMR和你画我猜那样一刀切... 她失去了大量粉丝，也失去了目标，主角会帮助她渡过难关吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/85335e4683716ada734b85b2ceb0495d.apng?t=1752205441\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/85335e4683716ada734b85b2ceb0495d.poster.avif?t=1752205441\" class=\"bb_img\" width=300 height=340 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/d51641fae6978adac94c31c2c73be1a0.poster.avif?t=1752205441\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/d51641fae6978adac94c31c2c73be1a0.webm?t=1752205441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆小鸟游芊穗是无敌的</strong></h2>芊穗是一个奇怪的虚拟主播，来自异世界的魔法使，在与魔王的战斗中使用时空之刃斩破了位面来到这里，「水晶之眼」想把她打上标签限制保护起来，「黑棺研究院」复苏魔王也需要她的能力，所以她需要粉丝的信仰给她补魔来对抗他们；当然没有人相信这些东西，只是觉得她一本正经的很搞笑，角色扮演的有点入戏或是中二病晚期...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/97ff2c5ea4d2c017a4c9b0726d990350.poster.avif?t=1752205441\" width=300 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/97ff2c5ea4d2c017a4c9b0726d990350.webm?t=1752205441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/2bf2dd4ad826142cdcf28e2a6ce53291.poster.avif?t=1752205441\" width=300 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/2bf2dd4ad826142cdcf28e2a6ce53291.webm?t=1752205441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆莜米_Official</strong></h2>莜米曾经是一名音乐区的唱见，在成为虚拟主播之前就有不少粉丝，在虚拟主播的形式出现后也制作了自己的虚拟形象；她性格胆怯，只有在唱歌时会没有任何顾虑，但也因此错过了很多机会，她与主角虽然有着不同的背景但是却有着相似的目标，也希望成为一名歌星，在选秀节目中脱颖而出，她能克服自己的内心吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/db06dd4bb22684f1545b50da3327ec1a.apng?t=1752205441\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/db06dd4bb22684f1545b50da3327ec1a.poster.avif?t=1752205441\" class=\"bb_img\" width=300 height=340 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/da4c250ec7022189f2959e86ba8f09ec.gif?t=1752205441\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/da4c250ec7022189f2959e86ba8f09ec.poster.avif?t=1752205441\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>开发者的话</strong></h2>这个游戏确实受到了《主播女孩重度依赖》与《VA-11 Hall-A》启发，我个人也非常喜欢这2款游戏，当然玩法和剧情是完全不同的，主要是像素太戳XP，通过主角达成的属性（唱功、杂谈力、技术力等）、其他角色之间的好感来触发不同的事件与结局，大部分内容是比较诙谐有趣的。<br>我是一个虚拟主播重度依赖症患者，当然在很多人眼里D的也不算多，也就几百个牌子吧？我大约是从19年D到现在的，也曾经想自己开个V箱，几乎见证了完整的V圈的转变，日V时代、国V崛起、角色扮演原教旨V的没落、人均整活劈叉、热水器时代、抽象V的诞生，还有今年吃到撑的各种瓜。<br>对于完全不了解虚拟主播和V圈的玩家，你也想了解V圈生态或者重温一些有趣的经典事件，游戏内也提供了解释笔记，记录了大部分的黑话和知名梗的解释，当然也可以自行选择关闭。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/0f119227ae0abb61bf5c0ca54aa62f5e.poster.avif?t=1752205441\" width=640 height=315 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289560/extras/0f119227ae0abb61bf5c0ca54aa62f5e.webm?t=1752205441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>如果您对这款游戏有兴趣，请点点愿望单<br><br>官方群：587103179",
